<section id="about" class="py-24 relative bg-slate-900/30">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="text-center mb-20">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-cosmic-400 to-blush-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
        About Me
      </h2>
      <div class="w-24 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-cosmic-400 to-blush-400 mx-auto rounded-full"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="bg-slate-800/30 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-8 border border-cosmic-500/20">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-cosmic-300">Who I Am</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Hi, I'm Manasvi. I'm a Computer Science student pursuing a dual degree, deeply passionate about backend systems and the endless possibilities of AI and machine learning. I love the challenge of building robust, scalable systems that power the applications we use every day. I find the integration between BioTech and Computer science endlessly fascinating.
          </p>
          <p class="text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
            When I'm not coding, you'll find me exploring the latest ML research papers, experimenting with new frameworks, or diving deep into system architecture patterns. I believe in writing clean, efficient code that not only works but tells a story. Apart from this, i enjoy astronomy, reading books and sketching.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-slate-800/30 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-8 border border-cosmic-500/20">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-blush-300">What Drives Me</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
            I'm fascinated by the intersection of elegant code and powerful functionality. Whether it's optimizing database queries, designing RESTful APIs, or training neural networks, I approach each challenge with curiosity and determination to find the most elegant solution. I enjoy crafting experiences for everyone.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-8">
        <div class="bg-slate-800/30 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-8 border border-cosmic-500/20">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-6 text-mint-300">Tech Stack</h3>
          
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-medium text-cosmic-300 mb-3">Full - Stack & Systems</h4>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                <span class="tech-tag">Python</span>
                <span class="tech-tag">React.js</span>
                <span class="tech-tag">Typescript</span>
                <span class="tech-tag">Django</span>
                <span class="tech-tag">Flask</span>
                <span class="tech-tag">Node.js</span>
                <span class="tech-tag">PostgreSQL</span>
                <span class="tech-tag">Neo4j.</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-medium text-blush-300 mb-3">AI & Machine Learning</h4>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                <span class="tech-tag">Neural Networks </span>
                <span class="tech-tag">ML Libraries </span>
                <span class="tech-tag">Scikit-learn</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-medium text-mint-300 mb-3">Tools & Cloud</h4>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                <span class="tech-tag">AWS & Azure</span>
                <span class="tech-tag">Docker</span>
                <span class="tech-tag">Git</span>
                <span class="tech-tag">Linux</span>
                <span class="tech-tag">Power BI</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-cosmic-500/20 to-blush-500/20 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-cosmic-400/30">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-white">Current Focus</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-slate-300">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-cosmic-400 rounded-full animate-pulse"></div>
              Completing my CS dual degree program
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-blush-400 rounded-full animate-pulse"></div>
              Exploring distributed systems architecture
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-mint-400 rounded-full animate-pulse"></div>
              Deep learning for natural language processing
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-cosmic-400 rounded-full animate-pulse"></div>
              Contributing to open-source ML projects
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .tech-tag {
    @apply px-3 py-1 bg-slate-700/50 text-slate-300 rounded-full text-sm font-medium border border-slate-600/30 hover:border-cosmic-400/50 hover:text-cosmic-300 transition-all duration-300 cursor-default;
  }
</style>